        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/skunk/scene_skunk.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 90505cde-9b68-488f-827b-ff81498264aa).Image",
        "Description": "So, 47, it looks like this candidate for the election isnt very liked. Well, more accurately, we dont like him. He&apos;s been collecting a lot of intel on you, and we cant have that. I know you dont care for politics, but you have to assasinate him and his associates. Two of which are disguised as normal civilians, and they&apos;re all in a public space. You can&apos;t get recorded, otherwise the risk of the world finding out about you increases exponentially. Good luck 47.",
